long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: CUB productivity app that allows Sienge ERP users to perform swift installment reconciliations. The app automatically identifies paid installments not yet integrated into the ERP and automatically marks them as reconciled improving the end user productivity and eliminating manual errors.
